data.title: Save up to $600 per person* on Bucket List Europe
data.meta_description: Save up to $600 per person* on Bucket List European holidays when you fly in early and fly out late! Offer ends 30 August. *T&Cs apply.
data.text:
See more of Europe on us!

See more of Europe on us.

Thanks to over 13 years’ experience, we know Europe better than anyone, and for a limited time, we’re making it even easier to spend more time in your favourite destination.

Until 30 August, when you book one of our incredible bucket list deals to Europe, you can fly in early and fly out late for free, saving up to $600 per person*! Simply select a date within 30 days of your tour or cruise, then book and save!

This amazing flexibility is available on our curated range of European Tours and Cruises that can take you to the streets of Rome, the fjords of Norway, the islands of Greece and more! Plus, if you prefer to bask in the summer sun or see Europe during the cooler months, we have holidays that depart year-round.

*Bucket List Europe Offer - Terms and Condition

During the promotional period of 11:00am Tuesday 6 August 2024 to 11:59pm Friday 30 August 2024 (AEST), customers can fly in early and fly out late for free and save up to $600 per person when they choose Arrive Early and Stay Behind options (save $300 per person per option) on select Tour and Cruise deals to Europe only as listed on www.tripadeal.com.au/campaign/bucket-list-europe. Customers do not have to select Arrive Early or Stay Behind options to travel on the selected Tour or Cruise, but must select a Arrive Early or Stay Behind options offer to qualify for savings. Offer only applies to new bookings made during the promotional period, does not apply to existing bookings. Arrive Early/Stay Behind options are subject to flight availability over a 30 day period before the tour starts and after the tour ends. Offer only applies to Arrive Early/Stay Behind options according to the arrival and departure city(s) listed on the applicable deal. Some dates within the 30 day period may not be available or may be sold out. Each available date that qualifies within the 30 day period will have a $300 saving applied. A high season surcharge may apply to some dates. The offer includes the cost of flights only as included in the Arrive Early/Stay Behind options, it does not cover extra nights of accommodation, meals, airport transfers, insurance, spending money, or any other travel related expenses. No flight booking changes or cancellations are permitted after air tickets have been issued. The offer can be used in conjunction with bookings made using Qantas Points. Customers will continue to earn the standard 3 Qantas Points per $1 spent on the total booking value. You must be a Qantas Frequent Flyer member to earn and use points. Qantas Frequent Flyer Membership is free and can be accessed via the Qantas website. The offer does not apply to Hotel Packages, Experiences, or any other deals unless advertised on the campaign page. Offer does not apply to associated travel services, concierge flight tickets, travel visas, or travel insurance. The offer can be used in conjunction with TripADeal Gift Certificates and vouchers. The offer is non-refundable, non-redeemable for cash, and cannot be used with any other offer/promotion unless otherwise stated. Offer excludes credit card surcharges. All deals and travel dates are subject to availability and may be sold out, or can be withdrawn or varied without notice. All bookings will be bound by the Terms and Conditions and Important Information of your selected deal. Payment is required in full, together with the redemption of the TripADeal offer. The offer must be used within the stated validity period. To redeem this offer, contact the TripADeal Sales and Service centre on 135 777 or book online at tripadeal.com.au. Qantas Points will be credited to a member's account up to 8 weeks after cruise or tour completion. Qantas Points will not be earned on cancelled bookings. Terms and conditions are subject to change at any time and without notice.
